1
00:00:51,385 --> 00:00:52,595
Kau selalu sakit.

2
00:00:54,221 --> 00:00:55,806
Kau sakit saat seusiaku.

3
00:00:59,184 --> 00:01:00,269
Malam, Pak.

4
00:01:01,895 --> 00:01:03,147
Malam, Victor.

5
00:01:03,230 --> 00:01:04,815
Aku tak tahu kau masih di sini.

6
00:01:06,692 --> 00:01:09,987
Hanya menemani
James, Pak, jika boleh.

7
00:01:12,156 --> 00:01:13,115
Baik sekali.

8
00:01:15,242 --> 00:01:18,245
- Sudah baikan, Nak?
- Masih kedinginan.

9
00:01:18,329 --> 00:01:20,998
Hanya demam ringan.
Besok pagi baikan.

10
00:01:21,081 --> 00:01:22,916
Ayah selalu bilang begitu.

11
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:26,545
- Dan selalu sembuh, 'kan?
- Ya.

12
00:01:26,629 --> 00:01:29,048
Obat sudah diminum?

13
00:01:30,716 --> 00:01:31,800
Elizabeth!

14
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:34,053
Elizabeth!

15
00:01:34,136 --> 00:01:35,721
Ayahmu mabuk lagi.

16
00:01:35,804 --> 00:01:37,848
- Kau harus bawa dia pulang, Victor.
- Elizabeth!

17
00:01:37,931 --> 00:01:40,225
Bukan namaku
yang dia panggil, Pak.

18
00:01:42,353 --> 00:01:43,771
- Ayah!
- Tetap di sana, James!

19
00:01:43,854 --> 00:01:45,773
- Lepaskan aku!
- Ayah!

20
00:01:46,857 --> 00:01:47,858
Lepaskan aku!

21
00:01:47,941 --> 00:01:50,110
Kau tak pernah
mencintainya! Ikut aku!

22
00:01:50,194 --> 00:01:52,112
Sudah kubilang
jangan datang lagi!

23
00:02:11,465 --> 00:02:13,092
James...

24
00:02:18,972 --> 00:02:20,516
Tidak...

25
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:21,892
James...

26
00:02:22,559 --> 00:02:24,353
- Ada hal yang tak kau pahami.
- Jangan.

27
00:02:24,436 --> 00:02:26,021
- Dia perlu tahu!
- Jangan!

28
00:02:26,105 --> 00:02:28,232
- Jangan bohong lagi.
- James...

29
00:02:46,458 --> 00:02:48,210
James!

30
00:02:53,549 --> 00:02:56,719
Dia bukan ayahmu...

31
00:03:04,935 --> 00:03:06,186
Nak.

32
00:03:15,070 --> 00:03:16,488
Kau ini apa?

33
00:03:31,670 --> 00:03:32,671
Aku tak bermaksud membunuhnya!

34
00:03:32,755 --> 00:03:34,214
Kau bermaksud melakukannya!

35
00:03:36,049 --> 00:03:37,676
Dia pantas dibunuh.

36
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,094
Dan kau melakukannya.

37
00:03:41,972 --> 00:03:43,599
Kita bersaudara, Jimmy.

38
00:03:43,682 --> 00:03:46,852
Sadarkah? Saudara
saling melindungi.

39
00:03:48,228 --> 00:03:51,440
Kau harus jadi kuat. Sangat
kuat agar tak tersentuh.

40
00:03:53,066 --> 00:03:55,861
- Aku ingin pulang.
- Tak bisa.

41
00:03:55,944 --> 00:03:57,654
Kita harus bersama,
apa pun yang terjadi.

42
00:03:58,322 --> 00:04:00,616
Bereskan siapa pun
yang menghalangi.

43
00:04:01,450 --> 00:04:02,826
Bisakah kau lakukan itu, adikku?

44
00:04:06,121 --> 00:04:07,414
Akan kucari di sungai!

45
00:04:08,123 --> 00:04:09,583
- Mereka datang.
- Kalian ke sana.

46
00:04:09,666 --> 00:04:11,001
- Bisa lari?
- Cepat!

47
00:04:15,214 --> 00:04:17,424
Terus lari. Jangan
lihat ke belakang.

48
00:05:22,239 --> 00:05:23,490
Saling memunggungi!

49
00:06:20,881 --> 00:06:22,341
Sudah cukup!

50
00:06:25,093 --> 00:06:26,428
Cukup!

51
00:06:42,402 --> 00:06:43,862
Mundur, Prajurit!

52
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,328
Victor!

53
00:06:54,456 --> 00:06:58,585
Mundur!

54
00:07:01,755 --> 00:07:03,173
Tidak!

55
00:07:29,282 --> 00:07:30,534
Siap...

56
00:07:31,535 --> 00:07:32,619
Bidik...

57
00:07:32,703 --> 00:07:34,037
Bangunkan jika sudah usai.

58
00:07:43,839 --> 00:07:45,132
Tembak!

59
00:07:51,263 --> 00:07:53,890
- Orang aneh!
- Dasar binatang!

60
00:07:54,474 --> 00:07:56,184
Aku Mayor William Stryker.

61
00:07:56,977 --> 00:07:58,979
Kalian dihukum karena
membunuh perwira senior.

62
00:08:00,147 --> 00:08:01,064
Benarkah?

63
00:08:02,149 --> 00:08:05,318
- Kami punya masalah dengan otoritas.
- Kendalikan diri.

64
00:08:06,486 --> 00:08:08,030
Pak.

65
00:08:08,113 --> 00:08:12,242
Sipir bilang hukuman tembak
sudah dilaksanakan pukul 10.00.

66
00:08:13,118 --> 00:08:15,037
- Bagaimana itu?
- Itu geli.

67
00:08:20,167 --> 00:08:21,501
Kalian lelah lari?

68
00:08:22,335 --> 00:08:24,629
Lelah sangkal sifat alami?

69
00:08:25,589 --> 00:08:27,591
- Apa pedulimu?
- Aku peduli.

70
00:08:29,009 --> 00:08:30,594
Aku tahu istimewanya kalian.

71
00:08:31,636 --> 00:08:32,846
Betapa berharganya.

72
00:08:37,059 --> 00:08:41,646
Dengar. Kalian bisa tetap
terkurung bagai orang aneh,

73
00:08:42,564 --> 00:08:43,899
atau ikut denganku.

74
00:08:44,733 --> 00:08:46,777
Aku bentuk tim khusus,

75
00:08:47,527 --> 00:08:48,862
dengan hak khusus.

76
00:08:50,197 --> 00:08:54,076
Sekarang katakan, kalian mau
benar-benar melayani negara?

77
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:12,219
Aku suka senjata ini lebih dari apa
pun di dunia. Mau tahu sebabnya?

78
00:09:12,302 --> 00:09:13,804
Tidak.

79
00:09:13,887 --> 00:09:15,764
Kenangannya.

80
00:09:15,847 --> 00:09:18,016
Memang besar,
sulit masuk pesawat.

81
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:21,520
Hunuskan di pernikahan mantanmu,

82
00:09:21,603 --> 00:09:24,022
mereka tidak akan
pernah melupakannya.

83
00:09:24,106 --> 00:09:25,774
Lucu, Wade.

84
00:09:25,857 --> 00:09:28,652
Kau pikir aku peduli
dengan hal itu.

85
00:09:29,361 --> 00:09:32,114
Mungkin ini tak mengintimidasi
seperti punya pistol,

86
00:09:32,197 --> 00:09:35,909
atau cakar, atau kuku
tangan tunawisma.

87
00:09:44,876 --> 00:09:46,044
Manikur?

88
00:09:46,128 --> 00:09:48,255
Victor, tenang.

89
00:09:50,590 --> 00:09:53,176
Fred punya tato
baru. Aku prihatin.

90
00:09:54,386 --> 00:09:56,513
Aduh, Fred, kau
baru kenal semalam.

91
00:09:57,597 --> 00:10:00,267
- Aku mencintainya.
- Setelah baru semalam?

92
00:10:00,350 --> 00:10:01,768
Dia pesenam.

93
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:04,896
Bradley, turunkan pesawat.

94
00:10:09,776 --> 00:10:11,903
Oh, tidak...

95
00:10:11,987 --> 00:10:12,988
Mau muntah?

96
00:10:13,071 --> 00:10:14,614
Jika ditakdirkan
terbang, kita bersayap.

97
00:10:14,698 --> 00:10:17,200
Jangan cemas, Nancy. Lebih banyak
yang tewas menyetir daripada naik pesawat.

98
00:10:17,284 --> 00:10:19,077
Kalau dengan tusukan?

99
00:10:19,161 --> 00:10:20,620
Bersikap baiklah.

100
00:10:20,704 --> 00:10:22,581
Atau bersikap
sebaik yang kau bisa.

101
00:10:24,124 --> 00:10:25,458
Butuh ember?

102
00:10:25,542 --> 00:10:28,336
Tuan-Tuan, tiba di
Lagos lima menit lagi.

103
00:11:03,997 --> 00:11:05,081
Kenapa kita ke sini?

104
00:11:05,874 --> 00:11:06,875
Nanti juga tahu.

105
00:11:07,542 --> 00:11:08,585
Zero?

106
00:11:13,757 --> 00:11:15,175
Penyusup!

107
00:11:15,258 --> 00:11:16,384
Pelanggaran wilayah!

108
00:11:16,468 --> 00:11:17,719
Siapkan senjata!

109
00:11:19,137 --> 00:11:20,889
Penyusup, setop!

110
00:11:21,765 --> 00:11:23,350
Tangan di belakang kepala!

111
00:11:52,963 --> 00:11:54,130
Sudah senang?

112
00:11:59,594 --> 00:12:01,429
- Fred.
- Tank-nya?

113
00:12:02,097 --> 00:12:03,723
Tank-nya.

114
00:12:03,807 --> 00:12:05,100
Akan kutangani.

115
00:12:39,801 --> 00:12:40,885
Bagus.

116
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:44,389
Terjebak di lift dengan lima
pria berdiet protein tinggi.

117
00:12:44,472 --> 00:12:46,016
- Wade.
- Mimpiku terwujud.

118
00:12:46,099 --> 00:12:48,143
Diam! Kau selanjutnya.

119
00:12:48,226 --> 00:12:50,353
Terima kasih, Pak. Kau tampan.

120
00:12:50,437 --> 00:12:52,897
Hijau pancarkan
keseriusan di matamu.

121
00:12:52,981 --> 00:12:54,858
Astaga. Kau bisa diam, tidak?

122
00:12:54,941 --> 00:12:56,818
Tidak saat aku terjaga.

123
00:12:57,944 --> 00:13:00,196
Bradley? Lantai teratas.

124
00:13:08,455 --> 00:13:09,706
Bidik liftnya!

125
00:13:09,789 --> 00:13:10,749
Liftnya!

126
00:13:21,009 --> 00:13:22,260
Waktunya kerja.

127
00:13:59,214 --> 00:14:00,465
Baiklah!

128
00:14:01,382 --> 00:14:02,801
Semua tewas!

129
00:14:05,136 --> 00:14:08,431
Jika tak banyak bicara, Wade,
kau akan jadi tentara sempurna.

130
00:14:14,646 --> 00:14:16,397
Tak akan kulakukan
jika aku jadi kau.

131
00:14:21,152 --> 00:14:22,320
Ambil berliannya.

132
00:14:23,446 --> 00:14:24,405
Semuanya milikmu.

133
00:14:24,489 --> 00:14:26,032
Aku tak mau berlian.

134
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,451
Aku mau ini.

135
00:14:29,410 --> 00:14:31,412
Tapi itu tak berharga.

136
00:14:31,496 --> 00:14:32,956
Suvenir.

137
00:14:33,039 --> 00:14:35,500
Di mana kau menemukannya?
Aku mau sumbernya.

138
00:14:36,876 --> 00:14:39,712
Desa kecil, di pedalaman.

139
00:14:40,380 --> 00:14:41,756
Tiga hari dari sini.

140
00:14:44,175 --> 00:14:47,762
Katakan batu ini lebih
berharga dari nyawanya.

141
00:14:47,846 --> 00:14:49,222
Tanya ditemukan di mana.

142
00:14:58,815 --> 00:15:00,483
Hei, hei, hei!

143
00:15:00,567 --> 00:15:01,693
Hei.

144
00:15:03,361 --> 00:15:04,737
Katanya datang dari langit.

145
00:15:09,075 --> 00:15:10,243
Dia jujur.

146
00:15:11,870 --> 00:15:13,246
Kau tak tahu bahasanya.

147
00:15:13,913 --> 00:15:15,915
- Itu pecahan meteor.
- Aku tahu itu.

148
00:15:15,999 --> 00:15:17,375
Tapi di mana ditemukannya.

149
00:15:18,459 --> 00:15:21,087
Pak, markas ingin
tahu lokasi kita.

150
00:15:21,171 --> 00:15:22,630
Hentikan mereka.

151
00:15:22,714 --> 00:15:23,798
Ya.

152
00:15:25,717 --> 00:15:27,760
Bilang semua di sini akan mati

153
00:15:27,844 --> 00:15:30,180
kecuali dia katakan di
mana batu ini ditemukan.

154
00:15:40,899 --> 00:15:42,692
Dia bilang itu suci.

155
00:15:42,775 --> 00:15:44,068
Baiklah.

156
00:15:47,614 --> 00:15:48,698
Victor.

157
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,091
Victor!

158
00:16:10,803 --> 00:16:12,305
Jangan coba-coba lakukan.

159
00:16:14,432 --> 00:16:16,226
Bukan ini tujuan kita ikut.

160
00:16:20,146 --> 00:16:21,397
Lepaskan dia!

161
00:16:34,327 --> 00:16:35,370
Apa yang kau lakukan?

162
00:16:37,372 --> 00:16:39,791
Situasi kita cukup bagus
sekarang, jangan mengacau.

163
00:16:39,874 --> 00:16:41,876
Sudah cukup, Victor.
Kita sudah berbuat cukup.

164
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:44,087
Kau pikir kau siapa?

165
00:16:44,170 --> 00:16:45,672
Ini pekerjaan kita.

166
00:16:46,589 --> 00:16:50,843
Mungkin kau lebih suka sembunyi
sampai mereka temukan cara bunuh kita?

167
00:16:53,346 --> 00:16:54,305
Aku muak.

168
00:16:57,141 --> 00:16:58,268
Kau ikut?

169
00:17:05,149 --> 00:17:06,109
Jimmy!

170
00:17:12,031 --> 00:17:13,616
Kami tak bisa biarkan kau pergi.

171
00:17:22,959 --> 00:17:24,085
Jimmy!

172
00:17:27,088 --> 00:17:28,131
Jimmy!

173
00:17:54,073 --> 00:17:56,951
PEGUNUNGAN ROCKY,
KANADA, ENAM TAHUN KEMUDIAN

174
00:18:17,847 --> 00:18:19,182
Kenapa bangun pagi-pagi?

175
00:18:22,352 --> 00:18:23,436
Kemarilah.

176
00:19:02,392 --> 00:19:03,518
Sampai nanti, Sayang.

177
00:19:05,186 --> 00:19:06,437
Hei.

178
00:19:13,319 --> 00:19:15,321
Bagus, ya.

179
00:19:18,157 --> 00:19:19,742
Kau dikendalikan wanita.

180
00:19:37,593 --> 00:19:39,345
Akan kumenangkan.

181
00:19:42,223 --> 00:19:43,641
Tidak. Ayo.

182
00:19:45,393 --> 00:19:47,061
Astaga!

183
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:49,188
Ayo naik Bianglala. Ayo.

184
00:19:49,730 --> 00:19:51,858
Luar biasa, wanita dalam kotak!

185
00:19:54,360 --> 00:19:56,654
MATIKAN LAMPUNYA

186
00:20:02,994 --> 00:20:04,745
Hei, ini tentang apa?

187
00:20:07,248 --> 00:20:09,417
Bisa matikan
lampu, dapat hadiah.

188
00:20:09,500 --> 00:20:10,918
Sedolar, tiga kali.

189
00:20:11,002 --> 00:20:12,503
Ayolah. Aku mau coba.

190
00:20:13,713 --> 00:20:14,755
Ini.

191
00:20:19,927 --> 00:20:21,429
Sudah jelas.

192
00:20:25,349 --> 00:20:26,517
Sudah dua kali.

193
00:20:35,568 --> 00:20:36,861
Itu trik konyol.

194
00:20:38,070 --> 00:20:39,447
Bukan trik, Kawan.

195
00:20:40,448 --> 00:20:42,867
Ayo. Dasar aneh.

196
00:20:44,452 --> 00:20:45,620
Dah!

197
00:21:14,106 --> 00:21:15,316
Pertunjukan selesai!

198
00:21:20,655 --> 00:21:23,199
Kubilang, pertunjukan selesai!

199
00:21:28,204 --> 00:21:30,122
Pertunjukan kita
tak pernah selesai.

200
00:21:33,376 --> 00:21:34,877
Victor.

201
00:21:34,961 --> 00:21:36,295
Tak mengajakku masuk?

202
00:21:38,381 --> 00:21:40,675
Ya. Masuklah.

203
00:21:53,437 --> 00:21:54,897
Aku tak pernah bilang

204
00:21:55,815 --> 00:21:58,234
pada siapa pun
tentang yang terjadi.

205
00:21:58,943 --> 00:22:01,529
Aku jalani hidup
beda sama sekali.

206
00:22:01,612 --> 00:22:03,114
Tak perlu ungkit masa lalu.

207
00:22:18,963 --> 00:22:20,089
Kau tahu...

208
00:22:21,674 --> 00:22:25,303
Aku selalu pikir bahwa
Wade-lah yang akan ketuk pintuku.

209
00:22:26,012 --> 00:22:27,263
Yah...

210
00:22:28,222 --> 00:22:29,557
Soal itu...

211
00:22:30,474 --> 00:22:31,684
Wade mati.

212
00:22:35,438 --> 00:22:37,064
Aku tak takut padamu.

213
00:22:40,192 --> 00:22:41,444
Aku tak takut mati.

214
00:22:43,612 --> 00:22:44,864
Bagaimana tahunya?

215
00:22:46,449 --> 00:22:47,992
Kau belum pernah coba.

216
00:23:05,843 --> 00:23:07,094
Mimpi perang?

217
00:23:09,221 --> 00:23:10,181
Yang mana?

218
00:23:11,223 --> 00:23:12,433
Semuanya.

219
00:23:20,649 --> 00:23:21,609
Ceritakan.

220
00:23:22,318 --> 00:23:23,527
Hei.

221
00:23:24,320 --> 00:23:25,780
Hanya tergores.

222
00:23:33,412 --> 00:23:35,706
Tampaknya kita
butuh seprai baru lagi.

223
00:23:36,624 --> 00:23:37,833
Ya.

224
00:24:02,566 --> 00:24:03,859
Siapa itu?

225
00:24:04,735 --> 00:24:06,195
Bau pemerintah.

226
00:24:10,866 --> 00:24:13,244
Astaga. Kau tak menua!

227
00:24:13,327 --> 00:24:14,412
Hidup sehat.

228
00:24:15,371 --> 00:24:16,831
Kau ingat Agen Zero?

229
00:24:16,914 --> 00:24:18,999
Masih tembak dulu,
tanya kemudian?

230
00:24:21,502 --> 00:24:23,295
Masih kunyah cerutu murah?

231
00:24:24,004 --> 00:24:25,673
Anak-Anak, tenang.

232
00:24:27,258 --> 00:24:29,468
- Ada pekerjaan untukmu.
- Sudah punya pekerjaan.

233
00:24:29,552 --> 00:24:31,595
Penebang pohon?
Delapan belas ribu setahun?

234
00:24:31,679 --> 00:24:33,139
Delapan belas lima ratus.

235
00:24:33,222 --> 00:24:35,099
Dan aku sudah lama
tidak membunuh orang.

236
00:24:35,182 --> 00:24:37,184
- Mulai rindu?
- Kini, ya.

237
00:24:37,268 --> 00:24:38,561
- Ya?
- Zero.

238
00:24:38,644 --> 00:24:39,854
Balik ke mobil.

239
00:24:43,107 --> 00:24:44,233
Anak pintar.

240
00:24:51,115 --> 00:24:53,742
Aku tak suka cara
hubungan kita berakhir.

241
00:24:54,535 --> 00:24:55,995
Perbincangan selesai.

242
00:24:57,538 --> 00:25:00,833
Main "Little House on the
Prairie" dengan guru sekolah,

243
00:25:01,500 --> 00:25:03,419
itu bukan dirimu, Logan.

244
00:25:03,502 --> 00:25:04,920
Memangnya kau tahu?

245
00:25:05,963 --> 00:25:07,298
Aku tahu.

246
00:25:07,381 --> 00:25:08,716
Apa maumu, Stryker?

247
00:25:10,634 --> 00:25:12,303
Bradley tewas tiga hari lalu.

248
00:25:14,096 --> 00:25:15,514
Wade sebelumnya.

249
00:25:16,515 --> 00:25:18,934
Ada yang memburu tim lama kita.

250
00:25:20,936 --> 00:25:22,438
Yang lainnya?

251
00:25:22,521 --> 00:25:24,356
