Senjata X di lumbung.

510
00:51:26,041 --> 00:51:27,835
Dia bunuh dua warga sipil.

511
00:51:27,918 --> 00:51:29,336
Ledakkan dia.

512
00:51:29,420 --> 00:51:31,005
Lihat apa dia bisa tahan.

513
00:51:54,778 --> 00:51:56,071
Jemput aku!

