518
00:53:51,687 --> 00:53:53,063
Naik!

519
00:54:24,053 --> 00:54:25,804
Naik, naik! Cepat!

520
00:54:44,656 --> 00:54:45,532
Zero!

521
00:54:48,994 --> 00:54:50,120
Zero, jawab!

522
00:54:53,832 --> 00:54:54,792
Zero?

523
00:55:01,131 --> 00:55:02,716
