524
00:55:02,800 --> 00:55:04,259
Entahlah.

525
00:55:04,343 --> 00:55:05,552
Aku terluka.

526
00:55:07,638 --> 00:55:09,348
Matikah dia? Matikah Logan?

527
00:55:14,520 --> 00:55:15,646
Zero, jawab!

528
00:55:20,567 --> 00:55:22,069
Kau coba membunuhku.

529
00:55:23,028 --> 00:55:24,029
Logan?

530
00:55:24,113 --> 00:55:25,155
Di mana Victor?

531
00:55:25,239 --> 00:55:26,532
Balik ke markas.

